AMOSPro Extensionlist by Claes Ahlberg
--------------------------------------

Introduction
------------
This is a small tool that lists your extensions in Amos Professional.
It's programmed in AMOS Professional and is all GUI (thanks to Pietro
Ghizzoni's GUI-Extension).
Keep this .readme-file as I have NOT included any other documentation!


