Manual
------
Usage:
Start AMOSPro Extensionlist with its icon or from CLI.

The buttons:

Load Default Configuration - Load the AMOSPro default configuration
S:AMOSPro_Interpreter_Config.

Load Other Configuration - Load any other AMOSPro configurationfile.

About - Just some info.

Iconify - Iconifies the window. Click the closegadget to uniconify.

Quit - Blows up your computer and crashes your harddrive!!!!  
       (Ha! Just kidding! It actully just melts your CPU.)

The listview:
Press the scrollarrows to scroll through the list.


